<p>We organize weekend workshops at colleges to teach students how to get involved. You can invite us to yours.</p>

<p>We want more college students to have the community knowledge and technical skills to participate in globally distributed software projects: Big ones, like
<a href="http://www.mozilla.com/firefox/">Firefox</a> and
