<a href="http://pyblosxom.bluesock.org/">PyBlosxom</a> and
<a href="http://rephial.org/">angband</a>.</p>

<p>You do <b>not</b> need to know how to program to contribute to free software. Open source projects need code, and they also need original art, testing, documentation, web design, and bug triaging.</p>

<p>Does that sound cool? We'll teach you. <a href="upcoming-events/">See if we're coming to your school soon</a> -- if not, <a href="upcoming-events/">contact us</a> to see if we can work together to run a workshop on your campus!</p>

